{
  "stem": "1363.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Don't forget that we had a very limited access to the public.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We weren't allowed to go out after dark.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, as I said, the restrictions came always worse and worse, where you weren't allowed to go to cinemas or to go to any of the amusements.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we only lived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We-- we didn't even cook ourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We still had our housekeeper, who was very decent to us, and so on.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, that was about the time in '43, '44, beginning of '44, when they brought out a law that [INAUDIBLE] those people who are not Hungarian citizens.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by that time, my father was in Brussels.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in '42, the Germans came to Brussel and took him to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you-- how did you find out that information?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got the letters back what we have sent him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, my mother's heart broke over the letters, which came back, because we knew that Brussels been taken by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And what my father only wrote in, in a flower language, if you know what I mean, that he had made himself an accident on his hands so that he could be as an invalid.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he thought that they're not going to take him away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Auschwitz, because they knew that the Jews are gathered in Brussels as well, the same way as everywhere else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they take them somewhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, he didn't know what Auschwitz-- I don't think so, that he knew what Auschwitz was or anything similar.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only after the war did I search for him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I got the notification from the Belgium Jewish Welfare that he-- he was taken to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
